  "description": "New creepers that can appear in the oceans! Discover the new items and increase the difficulty of the ocean.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Aquatic_Creepers/MP_AquaticCreepers_header.webp\" width=\"1400\" height=\"451\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod introduces a brand-new underwater threat: the <strong data-start=\"172\" data-end=\"191\">Aquatic Creeper</strong>! These creatures can now spawn in <strong data-start=\"228\" data-end=\"249\">oceans and rivers</strong>, adding extra danger to your aquatic adventures.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Ready to play with your friends on the best hosting?</strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/flashh\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Aquatic_Creepers/MP_AquaticCreepers_promo.webp\" width=\"1493\" height=\"187\" /></strong></a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">I recommend <a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/Flashh\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Bisect Hosting</strong></a> for playing with friends because of their high-quality, lag-free servers. You can install any CurseForge modpack or your custom mods without errors. Plus, their support is available 24/7 to help with any issues. Use my code <a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/Flashh\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>to get a 25% discount</strong></a> on your purchase.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Aquatic_Creepers/MP_AquaticCreepers_description.webp\" width=\"1400\" height=\"151\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>⚔️ Key Features:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Aquatic Creepers have <strong data-start=\"349\" data-end=\"368\">half the health</strong> of a normal creeper.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">They can detect players from up to <strong data-start=\"429\" data-end=\"447\">15 blocks away</strong> and will swim toward them.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">If they get close enough and stay near you for a few seconds&hellip; 💥 they explode!</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Their spawn rate is <strong data-start=\"582\" data-end=\"600\">low by default</strong>, but a <strong data-start=\"608\" data-end=\"623\">config file</strong> is included so players can adjust spawn frequency to their liking.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"687\" data-end=\"700\">✨ New Exclusive Item:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"724\" data-end=\"742\">Blue Gunpowder</strong>: dropped by Aquatic Creepers.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Can be used to craft a <strong data-start=\"800\" data-end=\"815\">Blue Charge</strong>, expanding your combat and crafting possibilities.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">With <strong data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"895\">Aquatic Creepers</strong>, the ocean will never feel safe again&hellip; Do you dare to dive knowing what lurks below?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Aquatic_Creepers/MP_AquaticCreepers_screenshot.webp\" width=\"1493\" height=\"123\" /></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1296/282/aquatic-creepers-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1493\" height=\"799\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1296/285/aquatic-creepers-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1493\" height=\"799\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1296/287/aquatic-creepers-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1493\" height=\"799\" /></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://discord.gg/X4BEeSByGU\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Aquatic_Creepers/MP_AquaticCreepers_d